{"type": "article", "id": 17917, "title": "金属家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-23T06:53:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150300oMwKdaDL05fRyVPC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自台湾的设计事务所 KANARI 带来的家用产品系列，包括灯具，时钟和开瓶器。共同点在于每一系列都有金、银、铜三种带有金属感的颜色，线条简明清晰，有古典式的优雅和现代气息。其中，挂钟像套在了几个圆环里，大小圆环的阴影通过灯光投射在墙面上，很有艺术感。目前时钟和开瓶器已可出售，<a href=\"http://www.studiokanari.com/#!shop/ccnu\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614493843ftDv21mpwYRGlI.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"449\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261449392fI9EnZ6gYJtRikF.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144939Urw3ckBAZ5EPgQ1V.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"475\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144940QbJgBGMWULuwn6mX.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"480\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144940NGPyuKr40qOiptC9.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"474\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}